data.description: PRICE DROP!...Just in time for our open house! Seller says SELL..and NOW! Welcome to one of the most highly sought after neighborhoods in all of Evans, Georgia . BRAND NEW ROOF ( 50 YEAR SHINGLES) INSTALLED 2021. BRAND NEW ENCAPSULATED CRAWLSPACE WITH DEHUMIDIFER TO REDUCE MOISTURE IN 2023. LPV FLOORING ADDED IN KITCHEN IN 2018. BERBER CARPET INSTALLED IN 2017. INSULATED ATTIC. NEST INSTALLED FOR ALL HEATING/COOLING EFFICIENCY. SMART KEY PAD ENTRY ON BACK DOOR. SMART PANEL INSTALLED FOR SPRINKLERS. This all brick two-story home with a side entry double car garage is sure to be the perfect fit for your family.  The sellers have taken care of every inch of this home and are sad to see her go. The backyard is fully fenced & extremely large with a number of stately mature trees surrounding the property. That's something a new home can never give you. The seller has renovated two bathrooms creating a more modern vibe to the home. The pictures do not do these spaces justice . The home is compartmentalized with a positive flow giving you the option to have both formal and informal spaces  based off of your lifestyle.  Please read through the sellers disclosure in detail to see how well this home has been maintained . Recently, the sellers paid a good bit of money for a proper vapor barrier system to be added in the crawl space as noted above. That's something you may not see on the initial viewing of the home but is such an imperative feature that makes this property stand out from the rest of the competition in our marketplace . Home is competitively priced to sell quickly due to the sellers life circumstances . Only Fully qualified buyers to view property. Seller is serious about selling . Timeframe is important to the overall deal of this transaction . If rooms sizes are important please measure those upon viewing .
